song_lyrics: Deh-paryant na munzāīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 1
Saraḷ saheje vartīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 2
Bas āpne vash rahīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 3
Antardraṣhṭi sadā dharīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 4
Harisukhe sukhiyā banīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 5
Mukti dehe ā pāmīe Swāmī (2)... Jem kaho 6
title: Jem kaho tem karīe Swāmī
